page.title: 20Conclusion/Credits.
page.content: During our study of the block we realised how very rural the region,and how little we really knew about this area so close to our village.The nature of the area made it very difficult to find topics of different types.We should like to sincerely thank all the people within our block for all their helpful co_operation. {Credits.} The following people from the village of Guilsfield completed this survey_ Mr.V.Carey (headmaster), Mr.T.Richards Mr.D.Williams,G.Mitchell, L.Gotto, J.Jones,D.Thomas,A.Breese,D.White, N.Waters,N.Winstanley,S.Evans, S.Jacques,L.Roberts,C.John,J.Gittins and J.Liddiatt.
